Title: CONGRESS: CONnection-oriented Group address RESolution Service  
Author: Tal Anker David Breitgand Danny Dolev Zohar Levy 
Note: Contact Author: Tal Anker:  Office  This work was supported by the Ministry of Science of Israel, grant number 032-7658  
Address: Jerusalem, Israel  Givat Ram, Jerusalem 91904, Israel  
